---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

import ContactCTA from '../components/ContactCTA.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Alex Abushady" description="About Alex Abushady's background.">
	<div class="stack gap-20">
		<main class="wrapper about">
			<Hero
				title="About"
				tagline="Thanks for stopping by. Read below to learn more about me and my background."
			>
				<!-- <img
					width="1553"
					height="873"
					src=""
					alt=""
				/> -->
			</Hero>

			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Background</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<p>
						As you may have gathered by now, my name is Alex Abushady; I am currently working as a Software Engineer for MSI. During my time at MSI, I've witnessed the company grow from a small team of just three developers (including myself) into a much larger organization with over 30 developers across multiple teams. As you might imagine, over that time, I've learned how to navigate both a small start-up environment and a larger, more structured environment that comes with being in a more seasoned, publicly traded company. This experience with scaling systems and solving complex technical problems sparked my interest in the similar challenges found in game development.
					</p>
					<br />
					<p>
						In recent years I've been drawn to game development, particularly the technical challenges of building tools and backend systems that power player experiences. My enterprise background in high-availability systems and performance optimization translates well to the demands of modern game services. I'm passionate about creating robust, scalable solutions that let developers focus on creativity while the infrastructure just works. Currently exploring game engines while building my own projects.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Skills</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<ul>
						<li>C#</li>
						<li>Python</li>
						<li>JavaScript</li>
						<li>TypeScript</li>
						<li>T-SQL</li>
						<li>ASP.NET MVC</li>
						<li>API Development</li>
						<li>Web Application Development</li>
						<li>Game Modding</li>
						<li>Azure DevOps</li>
						<li>Git</li>
						<li>LLM Fine-tuning</li>
						<li>LLM Merging</li>
						<li>Dataset Curation</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="section-title">Currently Exploring</h2>
				<div class="content">
				  <ul>
					<li>Unity Engine</li> 
					<li>C# for Games</li>
					<li>Game Physics</li>
					<li>Game Optimization</li>
					<li>Procedural Generation</li>
					<li>Multiplayer Networking</li>
					<li>Game Development</li>
					<li>Game Modding</li>
				  </ul>
				</div>
			  </section>
		</main>

		<ContactCTA />
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.about {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3.5rem;
	}

	img {
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 1.5rem;
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
	}

	section {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		color: var(--gray-200);
	}

	.section-title {
		grid-column-start: 1;
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		color: var(--gray-0);
	}

	.content {
		grid-column: 2 / 4;
	}

	.content :global(a) {
		text-decoration: 1px solid underline transparent;
		text-underline-offset: 0.25em;
		transition: text-decoration-color var(--theme-transition);
	}

	.content :global(a:hover),
	.content :global(a:focus) {
		text-decoration-color: currentColor;
	}

	.content ul {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		list-style-type: disc;
		padding-left: 1.2rem;
	}

	.content ul li {
		break-inside: avoid;
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.about {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 60% 1fr;
		}

		.about > :global(:first-child) {
			grid-column-start: 2;
		}

		section {
			display: contents;
			font-size: var(--text-lg);
		}

		.content ul {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
			column-gap: 1.5rem;
		}
	}
</style>
